'''Beeraha Laalaada'''

[[File:Hanging_Gardens_of_Babylon.gif|thumb|[[Beeraha Laalaada]] ee magaalada Baabiyloon wakhtigii maamulka [[Assiyriya]]nka.]]

[[File:Pergamon_Museum_Berlin_2007085.jpg|thumb|[[Gidaar]]ka weyn ee magaalada Baabiyloon.]]

[[Beeraha Laalaada]] ([[ingiriis]]: Hanging Gardens) ee magaalada [[Baabiyloon]] iyo [[gidaar]]ka magaalada Baabiyloon oo maanta ku beegan [[magaalo|magaalada Al-Hillal]] ee dalka [[Ciraaq]] waxay ka mid ahaayeen [[Todobada Layaab]] ee [[duni]]da.<ref>"[[Beeraha Laalaada]] ([[ingiriis]]: Hanging Gardens) ee magaalada [[Baabiyloon]]"</ref><ref>"[[magaalo|magaalada Al-Hillal]] ee dalka [[Ciraaq]]"</ref> Beerahan waxaa dhisay [[boqor|boqor Nebujadnesarkii 2aad]] (Nebuchadnezzar II) ee boqortooyadii [[Baabiylooniya]] markii taariikhdu ahayd qiyaastii [[C.H|sanadkii 600 C.H]], taasi oo sababtu ahayd in uu ku raali-geliyo [[xaas]]kiisa Amaytis.<ref>"Beerahan waxaa dhisay [[boqor|boqor Nebujadnesarkii 2aad]]"</ref> Beeraha laalaada waxay burubureen [[qarnigii 1aad]] [[C.D]] markii [[dhul gariir]] adag ku habsaday deegaanada magaalada Baabiyloon ee [[Mesobotaamiya]].<ref>"[[qarnigii 1aad]] [[C.D]] markii [[dhul gariir]]"</ref> 

[[Beer|Beeraha Laalaada]] waxay ku beernaayeen dhinacyada [[webi]]ga [[Furaat]] kuwaasi oo sudhnaa [[gidaar]] leh dhumuc [[mitir|25 mitir]] ah. 
=Xaqiiqada=

[[Dad]]ka qaar muran ayay ka keeneen in Beeraha laalaada jireen ayagoo ku sheegay sheeko khiyaali ah. Si kastaba ha ahaatee, [[taariikh]]yahan u dhashay qabiilka Jaaldiin<ref>"<ref name="history">''The Hanging Gardens of Babylon: the mysterious wonder of the ancient world''. article by Robin Fowler [where?]</ref>"</ref> (Chaldean) oo la odhan jirey Berossus, kaasi oo ku noolaa Giriiga [[qarni|qarnigii 4aad]] [[C.H]] ayaa si fiican u sharaxay beeraha laalaada ee magaalada [[Baabiyloon]].<ref>"<ref name="history"/> Also recently, there have been digs on the banks of the [[Euphrates]] River of some large 25 meter-thick walls.<ref name="history"/>"</ref> 

Dhinaca kale, [[cilmi]]baadhis iyo dhul qodaal ay sameeyeen guuto aarkiyoolojiis ah waxaa lagu ogaaday in beeraha laalaada si dhab ah u jireen wakhtiyadii ay dhisnayd magaalada [[Baabiyloon]]. 

